  "title": "Resident Engineer C&S Jurong Island",
  "description": "<p>We’re Hiring: <strong>Resident Engineer C&S Jurong Island  </strong></p><p>Working Hours:  6 days per week, Mon to Sat.</p><p>Start Date: 1 to 2 month Notice period can apply !<br /></p><p><strong>*Job Description: *</strong></p><p><strong>The responsibility of the RE (Civil & Structural) </strong></p><p>• Assist QP(S) in the daily supervision and coordination duties including civil and structural works, site investigations, building works. </p><p>• Lead, monitor and supervise RTOs on Site. </p><p>• Responsible for the consistency of quality assurance inspections and testing for works. </p><p>• Attend site meetings and resolve technical issues with Contractor. </p><p>• Keep quality records of all works, monitor & report on work progress. </p><p>• Review and comment on contractor’s submissions. </p><p>• To check and verify reports, variations and progress claims submitted by contractors, including as built quantity for the variations. </p><p>• To undertake any other duties related to the project as and when instructed by the Engineer. </p><p>• To prepare and submit daily, weekly and monthly reports of site progress. </p><p>• To carry out any other works as reasonably deemed to be the scope of an RE (Civil & Structural) in the industry.<br /></p><p><strong>RE (Civil & Structural) - Qualifications.</strong></p><p>• Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Post Graduate Diploma, Professional Degree in Civil / Structural Engineering or equivalent. </p><p>• Registered as RE (C&S) with the Joint Accreditation Committee of the Institution of Engineers Singapore / Association of Consulting Engineers Singapore. </p><p><strong>• Minimum 10 years of experience in C&S works as a Resident Engineer in building projects. </strong></p><p>• Excellent problem-solving skills and ability to make quick, informed decisions. </p><p>•<strong> Familiar with steel structure and piling inspection, piling load test and excavation works. </strong></p><p>• Possess strong initiative, and ability to work independently and within team environment when required. </p><p>• Good interpersonal, written and verbal communication skills. <br /></p><p><strong>Work Location: Jurong Island</strong></p>",
